The University of Matanzas "Camilo Cienfuegos" (Spanish: Universidad de Matanzas "Camilo Cienfuegos", UM) is a university located in Matanzas, Cuba. It was founded in 1972 and is organized in 6 Faculties.


== Organization ==
These are the 6 faculties in which the university is divided into:

Faculty of Agriculture
Faculty of Social Sciences and Humanities
Faculty of Physical Education
Faculty of Engineering - Economics
Faculty of Informatics
Faculty of Chemistry - Mechanics


